Add `AsyncPromiseValidationFn`, `AsyncPromiseValidationOpts` as described in this document https://mongoosejs.com/docs/validation.html

Permits the following

```js
new Schema({
  promiseValidated: {
    type: Number,
    validate: {
      validator: async (val: number) => {
        return val === 2;
      }
    }
  },
})
```

